Quickstrike:





Quickstrike paused. He thought for a few seconds there was battle outside 
the base. He could almost feel it. He bolted from there.

"Scorponok, come wit' me!"  he called. The ran to the ramp, letting it open, 
then saw the battle. And there, was Transulus. He stood, eyeing the battle 
carefull, looking for the mouse. He focused his optics, looking past the 
Predacons, even Transulas. He looked to the right, by the trees was limp 
body of the mouse-bot.

Quickstrike charged off. "Auto-guns, on-line." he commaded. They came to 
attention, firing at Maximal signatures. He ran to the direction of Dark 
Mouse. "Hey!" he called out to her. "Hey you!" He came to a skidding hault 
by her side.
